Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…天梯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定到最大威脅對象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先進行排除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測Striker已將目標更新為加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾大人會從根本上為我們消除威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的援軍來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 形勢會被扭轉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先攻下那座遺跡島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到那些兵器…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在能量被大炮吸走之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾的手下可全都聚到下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正符合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一會兒 這座炮塔就會像氣球一樣炸裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會蠢到讓這東西落到他們手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這我行我素只懂耍帥的蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話 給我到展望台上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到達加爾剛蒂亞還有318秒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要截住它！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬆開！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂喂 那要怎麼辦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 加爾剛蒂亞的大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把那座塔給轟飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別開玩笑了 這可是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我數5下 你就跳下來
